382
00:21:57,548 --> 00:22:01,248
Did you see any suspicious people watching this house?

383
00:22:01,248 --> 00:22:04,048
No. We were burglarized twice.

384
00:22:04,048 --> 00:22:05,748
But nothing happened after that.

385
00:22:05,748 --> 00:22:07,148
Burglarized?

386
00:22:07,148 --> 00:22:10,348
Yes. The burglar broke in through the window.

387
00:22:11,348 --> 00:22:13,648
Ai, don't tell me that the burglary is...

